{"tid":1091344,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"比家用係人情 唔比係理所當然？？？","createTime":"2019-04-04T05:15:42.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-08T15:31:30.000Z","uid":19207,"like":20,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"1fb7f656769d527ca0cc4760ac140d46bea587a8","tid":1091344,"uid":19207,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-04T05:15:42.000Z","msg":"雖然我好感激你既養育之恩，但係你要我養你一世未免太過自私。家用我只會將正式咁比，我自己唔洗生活，為我將來打算？你可以話我自私，但係你唔為子女打算，生左出黎就算，由細到大都灌輸俾家用呢種觀念。咁咪仲自私？<br />\n唉，好迷惘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"129911e0b696053cd32ded3a51bad384f38ddf1a","tid":1091344,"uid":196712,"like":20,"dislike":1,"score":19,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-04T05:17:12.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"bbb033bf76281b5cbddf7165d2332c0ea23122c6","tid":1091344,"uid":117534,"like":6,"dislike":2,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-04T05:19:50.000Z","msg":"養兒防老心態，垃圾中國思想"},{"pid":"0dc3750819f980be3b086c6a2f713fffbb5e1f73","tid":1091344,"uid":229212,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-04T05:20:08.000Z","msg":"如果父母冇工作能力/退咗休，應該要比家用"},{"pid":"4bd23dd7ffa20cc3136a2da4bd46630fa4b8d2c6","tid":1091344,"uid":196924,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-04T05:21:43.000Z","msg":"一齊住咪俾<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"191a9f20a344fdf89303a9b4cf3a174a922cc634","tid":1091344,"uid":49285,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-04T05:22:19.000Z","msg":"如果住埋一齊 咁水電煤你都有份用 俾少少係應該<br />\n多與少視乎自己收入同兩老對你好唔好啦"},{"pid":"f5d7a1fd556cbe360712abb33d50869d357e38c0","tid":1091344,"uid":19207,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"129911e0b696053cd32ded3a51bad384f38ddf1a","tid":1091344,"uid":196712,"like":20,"dislike":1,"score":19,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-04T05:17:12.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"r